In the MATTER OF REGISTRANT M.G. Application for Judicial Review of Order Classifying Registrant and Establishing Registration and Notification Obligations (M.G. - Petitioner) C-285 September Term 2018
081744 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 2, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000142-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
